com.sciencesakura.dbsetup.csv

Class Import.Builder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sciencesakura.dbsetup.csv.Import.Builder
  • Enclosing class:
    Import

    public static class Import.Builder
extends Object
    A builder to create the Import instance.

    This builder can be used only once. Once it has built Import instance, builder's methods will throw an IllegalStateException.
